data.description: Back on the market!!! Buyer’s financing fell through. Their loss is your gain. Come check out this charming Move In Ready 3 bedroom 2 bath block home located on an oversized lot with mature landscaping. This newly updated home features New Interior and Exterior paint throughout, New waterproof laminate flooring in the living and dining areas, tile in the kitchen and baths, New lighting throughout, New ceiling fans in the living room and patio areas, New dining chandelier, Newly remodeled guest bathroom and New pedestrian garage door. Located minutes from Rainbow River, Rainbow Springs State Park, Downtown Dunnellon and a short drive to Ocala and The World Equestrian Center.
